high_descs: Turn right and walk around the coffee table and go all the way to the right corner of the room where the TV is.
Pick up the yellow object in front of the TV.
Turn left and walk around the chairs to the back of them where the floor lamp is.
anns.task_desc: Look at an object by the light of a lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and go around the table, through the doorway, and into the living room, then walk across the living room to the entertainment stand.
Pick up the yellow vase, on the entertainment stand, in front of the TV.
Move over to the lamp on your right.
Turn the lamp on while holding the vase.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the lamp in the living room.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the wall, turn left and walk to the wall, turn left move forward then hand right to walk through the entry way and cross the room to the TV stand.
Pick up the yellow vase that is sitting on the TV stand
turn around and cross the room, after passing the chairs take a left and then take another left to round the chairs and walk to the tall floor lamp
Lift the vase up and turn on the lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine a vase under a tall lamp
